>[Question]
>HI, I WOULD LIKE TO KNOW HOW I CAN FIGURE OUT THE ORIGINAL AMOUNT IF 
>I ONLY KNOW THE NET AMOUNT AFTER THE DISCOUNT. I KNOW WHAT THE 
>DISCOUNT RATE WAS. THANKS FOR YOUR HELP. THE PRICE IS 35.88  AND I 
>KNOW THAT I GOT A 25% DISCOUNT.
>
>[Difficulty]
>TO CONVERT THE PERCENTAGE
>
>[Thoughts]
